Extend the duration of your running deployment.  <pre><code>curl -X POST "https://app.nexlayer.io/extendDeployment" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "applicationName": "My AI App",
    "sessionToken": "your-session-token"
  }'
</code></pre> <pre><code>const extension = await client.extendDeployment("My AI App");
console.log(extension.message);
</code></pre>

Monitor the status of your deployment's pods.  <pre><code>curl -X POST "https://app.nexlayer.io/getPodsStatus" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "sessionToken": "your-session-token",
    "applicationName": "My AI App"
  }'
</code></pre> <pre><code>const status = await client.getPodsStatus("My AI App");
console.log(status.pods);
</code></pre>
